	<tr>
		<td class=subject><div class="subject"> Step4</div></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<table width="100%" border=0 cellpadding=1 cellspacing=0>
			<tr><td width="1%" nowrap valign=top>投稿者：</td><td width="99%" colspan=2><b><em><b>Lucifel</b> [管理者]</em></b> さん　　<span style="font-size:80%;">( uid , posts:13, since 2001/01/02 )</span>
</td></tr>
			
			
			<tr>
				<td nowrap valign=top>投稿日：</td>
				<td>2001/01/05 (金) 13:14</td>
				<td align=right nowrap>
					No.13 | 
					<a class=link href="wwwforum.cgi?id=1&az=edit&number=13">編集</a> | 
					<a class=link href="wwwforum.cgi?id=1&az=delete&number=13">削除</a> 
				</td>
			</tr>
			</table>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<div class=content>
			<p><a href="wwwforum.cgi?id=1&az=msg&number=9">記事No.9</a> へのコメントです。</p>

			<p></p>Step 4:<BR>This part gets a bit tricky. Garadain says the knife was good but its not quite up to his specs so he wants a <BR>coldain smithing hammer to fix the knife. speaking with him further he says that Tain Frostbight has one. <BR>Garadain gives you a note to Tain (which appears to be useless). when asked about Tain, Garadain says he <BR>left a short time ago to settle a score with a certain Kromrif. Head down to -4900, -2500 (or very close to <BR>there). Tain spawns there. but his last name is not Frostbight like Garadain said. its Tain Frosthammer or <BR>something. (he is on about a 40 minute timer). when hailed he says he is in trouble and needs help. do not tell him you will help him til you are buffed up and ready for a battle! When you tell Tain you will help him, he says that Khrak is coming for him with his war party. The giants spawn when you tell him you will help him. Just east, near the bridge, 4 giants spawn. one being Khrak. you need to kill Khrak and get the frost elixir off of him. Give Tain the Frost elixir and he will give you the coldain smithing hammer. return to Garadain and give him the hammer and the gold ring and he will return to you the Platinum Coldain Insignia Ring (you guessed it... 4ac 4str 4magic).<BR><BR>GaradainはKnifeを気に入ったものの、彼の要求をみたす性能ではないために、鍛えなおしたいと言ってきます。<BR>それにはcoldain smithing hammerが必要で、Tain Frostbightが1つ持っているとのこと。<BR>GaradainはTainへの手紙を渡してきます。<BR>彼にTainのことを尋ねると<BR>「he left a short time ago to settle a score with a certain Kromrif. 」との返事。<BR>Tainを探しにいきましょう。<BR>-4900,-2500にTainはSpawnします。しかしTainのLast NameがFrostbightではありません。<BR>TainにHailをすると、事件に巻き込まれているのでHelpが欲しいといってきます。<BR>Helpをすると答えると、「Khrak is coming for him with his war party.」といわれ、ちょうど東のところにGiantが4匹Spawnします。そのうちの1体がKhrakで、彼を殺してfrost elixirを入手しましょう。<BR>frost elixirをTainに渡すと、coldain smithing hammerを貰えます。<BR>coldain smithing hammerとgold ringをGaradainに渡すと、Platinum Coldain Insignia Ring(4AC,4STR,4MR)を入手できます。<BR><BR>#Garadainから貰ったTainへの手紙って意味なし?(^-^;<p></p>
			[ <a class=link href="wwwforum.cgi?id=1&az=reply&parent=13">この記事にコメントを返信する</a> ] [ <a class=link href="wwwforum.cgi?id=1&az=reply&parent=13&quote=auto">原文引用</a> ]
			</div>
